decks.notes: The deck focuses on a fast-paced aggressive strategy utilizing the partner commanders Rograkh and Silas Renn. With a mix of efficient removal, disruption, and powerful creatures, the deck aims to apply early pressure on the opponent while controlling the board and disrupting their game plan. The deck includes a wide range of versatile spells such as counterspells, removal, and card draw to maintain tempo and keep the pressure on the opponent. By combining aggressive creatures with disruptive and reactive spells, the deck aims to quickly overwhelm the opponent and secure victory through a combination of combat damage and disruption.

The deck focuses on utilizing Lier, Disciple of the Drowned's ability to cast instants and sorceries from the graveyard to control the game and disrupt the opponent's strategy. The key strategy is to generate mana advantage with cards like High Tide and Extraplanar Lens, while also leveraging counter spells like Force of Will and Cryptic Command to protect Lier. The deck includes card draw and tutor effects to find key pieces quickly, as well as disruption spells like Into the Flood Maw and Exhaustion to stall the opponent's tempo. With a high number of cheap spells and a focus on control, the deck aims to overwhelm the opponent with efficient plays and efficient card advantage.
